Day 1 : Board train from chennai to varkala
Sleeper 430/- . You will reach varkala at 11:00am

Grab a lunch or brunch and then head to the varkala cliff / black beach - 4.2kms from Railway station

Check in refresh yourself and go for a sunbath.
Between 6:00 - 6:45pm you could see a beautiful sunset and post that you can go for a walk enjoying different cuisines and cafes alongside.

For dinner we chose cafe Italiano. We had
1. Schezwan chicken fried rice - 230/-
(The quantity was huge and sufficient for 2)
2. Mahi mahi fish fry - 400/- (must try)

End the day with some shopping and ice creams

Day 2 : wake up head to the beach for water activities or for a morning walk
Hangouts at a cafe for Breakfast and checkout.

At 9:55am there is a train to kollam from varkala station. Ticket price - 35/- and you will reach kollam by 10:40am

The train to chennai (kollam express) is at 12:00pm until then you can relax.

Enjoy your journey with beautiful views and tunnels especially the *13 Arch bridge* till you reach tenkasi and post that it's a normal train travel

DM for more queries
